text: Canan or Janan is a Turkish female name from Persian origin, meaning beloved, it may refer to: ==Given name== * Aslı Canan Sabırlı (born 1991), Turkish women's footballer * Canan Dağdeviren (born 1985), Turkish materials scientist and academic * Canan Ediboglu, Turkish businesswoman * Canan Öztoprak, Turkish Cypriot politician ==Surname== * Samuel Canan, 34th Governor of American Samoa ==See also== * Cannan * Canaan * Canan (film) Category:Turkish feminine given names
title: Canan
